Abraham on missed pen: &quot;I&rsquo;m always someone who believes in myself in penalties. I had a few last season and a few important ones. Unfortunately I missed one of the most important ones for Chelsea. It&rsquo;s about how I react and just get my head up.&quot;<br />
<br />
&ldquo;The boys have made it feel like nothing has even happened. Everyone had their arms around me. They&rsquo;ve said the best players miss, it&rsquo;s something to learn from. It&rsquo;s better it happened now than later on. You grow into a man and learn from it.&rdquo;

